question: Within a radius of 180 kilometers, where can I find  a restaurant from Gary Lapelusa Landscaping LLC, Bayonne, NJ towards Wantagh Museum, NY?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.122011 40.662412)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.510278 40.680556)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.122011 40.662412)',4326)::geography, 180000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.122011 40.662412)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
